Quoting Text

Code

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8" />

<title>Quoting Text</title>

</head>

<body>

<p>He enjoyed this selection from <cite>The Adventures of Huckleberry
Finn</cite> by Mark Twain:

<blockquote
cite="http://www.marktwainbooks.edu/the-adventures-of-huckleberry-finn/">

<p>We said there warn't no home like a raft, after all. Other places do
seem so cramped up and smothery, but a

raft don't. You feel mighty free and easy and comfortable on a raft.</p>

</blockquote>

<p>It reminded him of his own youth exploring the county by river.</p>

</body>

</html>

