</head>

<body>

<p>The contestant was asked to spell "pleonasm." She requested the
definition and was told that <dfn>pleonasm</dfn>

means "a redundant word or expression" (Ref: <cite><a href="
http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/pleonasm"

rel="external">dictionary.com</a></cite>).</p>

