[[file:media/image69.png]]

Resetting or Normalizing Default Styles

Code

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="utf-8" />

<title>photobarcelona - Liz Castro's photographs and blog about
Barcelona</title>

