[[file:media/image77.png]]

Aligning Elements Vertically

Code

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="utf-8" />

<title>photobarcelona - Liz Castro's photographs and blog about
Barcelona</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/vertical-align.css" />

<!--[if lt IE 9]>

<script
src="http://html5shiv.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>

<![endif]-->

</head>

<body>

<div id="container">

