Choosing Your Markers

Code

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="utf-8" />

<title>Choosing Your Markers</title>

<style>

/* As always, place your CSS in an external file instead of embedding it
(it's embedded here to simplify the demo). */

li {

list-style-type: upper-roman;

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<h1>The Great American Novel</h1>

<ol>

<li>Introduction</li>

<li>Development</li>

<li>Climax</li>

<li>Denouement</li>

<li>Epilogue</li>

</ol>

</body>

</html>

