Choosing Where to Start List Numbering

Code

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="utf-8" />

<title>Choosing Where to Start List Numbering</title>

</head>

<body>

<h1>Changing a light bulb (with a few steps missing)</h1>

<ol start="2">

<li>Unscrew the old bulb.</li>

<li value="5">Screw in the new bulb.</li>

<li>Plug in the lamp and turn it on!</li>

</ol>

</body>

</html>

